DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Ship Mode])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Ship Mode], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Ship Mode]

DEFINE VAR __DS0FilterTable = 
	TREATAS({"Standard Class"}, 'SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Ship Mode])

EVALUATE
	SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
		__DS0FilterTable,
		"SumSales", IGNORE(CALCULATE(SUM('SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Sales])))

			'LocalDateTable_6ae07376-029d-4b2a-8d3f-f3b0835c5cbc'[Year],
			__DS0FilterTable,
			"SumSales", CALCULATE(SUM('SuperStore_Sales_Dataset'[Sales]))
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			SUMMARIZE(
				__DS0Core,
				'LocalDateTable_6ae07376-029d-4b2a-8d3f-f3b0835c5cbc'[Month],

		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'LocalDateTable_6ae07376-029d-4b2a-8d3f-f3b0835c5cbc'[Year])

		TOPN(

			1
		)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'LocalDateTable_6ae07376-029d-4b2a-8d3f-f3b0835c5cbc'[Year],
				ASC

metrics.visualTitle: Sum of Total Sales by Order Date

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'SalesForecast'[Order Date],
			"SumTotal_Sales", CALCULATE(SUM('SalesForecast'[Total Sales]))
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			'SalesForecast'[Order Date],
			[SumTotal_Sales],
			350,
			,
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
	"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount
)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyBinnedSample

ORDER BY
	'SalesForecast'[Order Date]
